<paragraph blockId="7.[189,1399,788,920]" pageId="7" pageNumber="169">
We provisionally assess 
<taxonomicName authority="Lin &amp; Guo &amp; Zhou &amp; Liao &amp; Mao, 2022" authorityName="Lin &amp; Guo &amp; Zhou &amp; Liao &amp; Mao" authorityYear="2022" box="[488,755,788,814]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Aspleniaceae" genus="Asplenium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="169" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="danxiaense" status="sp. nov.">
