</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[766,861,788,814]" pageId="7" pageNumber="169" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
as Critically Endangered based on criterion D of 
<bibRefCitation author="IUCN" box="[256,413,823,849]" pageId="7" pageNumber="169" refId="ref4599" refString="IUCN. 2012. IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria: Version 3.1. Second edition. Gland, Switzerland. Available from https: // portals. iucn. org / library / node / 10315 [accessed 5 November 2021]." type="url" year="2012">IUCN (2012)</bibRefCitation>
. Only one population and fewer than 50 individuals of 
<taxonomicName authority="Lin &amp; Guo &amp; Zhou &amp; Liao &amp; Mao, 2022" authorityName="Lin &amp; Guo &amp; Zhou &amp; Liao &amp; Mao" authorityYear="2022" box="[1087,1254,823,849]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Aspleniaceae" genus="Asplenium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="169" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="danxiaense" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[1087,1254,823,849]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="169">A. danxiaense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1261,1354,823,849]" pageId="7" pageNumber="169" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
are known from Danxia mountain. It was not seen by one of us during separate expeditions to nearby sites on Danxia mountain.
</paragraph>
